1. Installation

	Install this application in a directory of your choice.

2. Running the interface builder

	Start the shell script 'vdx', which is in the directory 'bin' of
	the installed tree. This script will setup the environment and
	call the real binary.

3. Deinstallation

	Remove this directory.


